::Kluster::

Kluster nods at Phobia's comment. "True."

He looks over at Hysteria, grinning. "You wern't notified because you 
obvioustly decided to take a long nap at the time. Savanah is right, though, 
the engines were less important that the whole crew."

He looks forward, seeing The Cybertronian Fire in front of them.

"Welcome to my ship," he says to the bots behind him, speeding up toward the 
entrance.
